message.raw: fix Time tests in common.  This is due to the change in behavior where Time*Time (or Time/Time) used to do a non-physical pair-wise operation on its elements sec and nsec (i.e. Time1*Time2 = Time(Time1.sec*Time2.sec, Time1.nsec*Time2.nsec), but now it's doing the proper multiplication and division between time values.  The regression tests are updated accordingly.
